Package org.lfj.lang.op

Class MathematicalFunction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.lfj.lang.Combiner
      • org.lfj.lang.Quasiapplicative
        • org.lfj.lang.Applicative
          • org.lfj.lang.ExpressionApplicative
            • org.lfj.lang.op.PrimitiveFunction
              • org.lfj.lang.op.MathematicalFunction
  • public class MathematicalFunction
extends PrimitiveFunction
    A class of functions that deal with all the mathematical functions defined by the java virtual machine including all arithmetic, logic, and cast operations. This operations are generalized so that they produce the appropriate instruction based upon their arguments making them generic.
